    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriate for Gradation 1 at this risk level. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index (RH < 1) acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five evaluated operating points, supporting the regulatory submission decision.",
